    'pakora': { protein: 2, carbs: 10, fiber: 1, fat: 8, unit: 'piece' },
    'bhaji': { protein: 2, carbs: 12, fiber: 1, fat: 6, unit: 'piece' },

    // Oils (mainly fat, minimal protein/carbs/fiber)
    'olive oil': { protein: 0, carbs: 0, fiber: 0, fat: 1, unit: 'gram' },
    'coconut oil': { protein: 0, carbs: 0, fiber: 0, fat: 1, unit: 'gram' },
    'sunflower oil': { protein: 0, carbs: 0, fiber: 0, fat: 1, unit: 'gram' },
    'mustard oil': { protein: 0, carbs: 0, fiber: 0, fat: 1, unit: 'gram' },
    'groundnut oil': { protein: 0, carbs: 0, fiber: 0, fat: 1, unit: 'gram' },
  };

  function parseFoodEntry(entry) {
    if (!entry) return { food: entry, protein: 0, carbs: 0, fiber: 0, fat: 0 };
    const parts = entry.split(' ');
    let name = parts[0];
    let qty = 1;
    let unit = '';

    // Multi-word food names
    if (foodData[entry]) {
      name = entry;
    } else if (foodData[parts.slice(0,2).join(' ')]) {
      name = parts.slice(0,2).join(' ');
      if (parts.length > 2) {
        // e.g. brown bread 2 slice
        const num = parseFloat(parts[2]);
        if (!isNaN(num)) qty = num;
        if (parts.length > 3) unit = parts[3];
        else unit = parts[2].replace(/[0-9]/g, '');
      }
    } else {
      // e.g. rice 200g
      if (parts.length > 1) {
        const num = parseFloat(parts[1]);
        if (!isNaN(num)) qty = num;
        unit = parts[1].replace(/[0-9]/g, '');
      }
    }

    // Default units
    if (foodData[name]) {
      unit = foodData[name].unit;
    }

    // Special handling for rice and bread
    if (name === 'rice' && unit.includes('g')) {
      // qty is already in grams
      const data = foodData['rice'];
      return {
        food: entry,
        protein: +(data.protein * qty).toFixed(2),
        carbs: +(data.carbs * qty).toFixed(2),
        fiber: +(data.fiber * qty).toFixed(2),
        fat: +((data.fat || 0) * qty).toFixed(2)
      };
    }
    if (name === 'brown bread' && unit.includes('slice')) {
      // Use slice nutrition
      const data = foodData['brown bread slice'];
      return {
        food: entry,
        protein: +(data.protein * qty).toFixed(2),
        carbs: +(data.carbs * qty).toFixed(2),
        fiber: +(data.fiber * qty).toFixed(2),
        fat: +((data.fat || 0) * qty).toFixed(2)
      };
    }
    // Default: per piece
    const data = foodData[name] || { protein: 0, carbs: 0, fiber: 0, fat: 0 };
    return {
      food: entry,
      protein: +(data.protein * qty).toFixed(2),
      carbs: +(data.carbs * qty).toFixed(2),
      fiber: +(data.fiber * qty).toFixed(2),
      fat: +((data.fat || 0) * qty).toFixed(2)
    };
  }

  const handleCalculate = () => {
    const resultArr = [
      { time: 'Morning', ...parseFoodEntry(morningFood) },
      { time: 'Evening', ...parseFoodEntry(eveningFood) },
      { time: 'Post Evening', ...parseFoodEntry(postEveningFood) },
      { time: 'Night', ...parseFoodEntry(nightFood) },
    ];
    setResults(resultArr);
  };

  // Get list of all food names for autocomplete
  const foodNames = Object.keys(foodData);

  // State for showing suggestions
  const [activeSuggestion, setActiveSuggestion] = useState(null);

  // Filter suggestions based on input
  const getSuggestions = (input) => {
    if (!input) return [];
    const inputLower = input.toLowerCase();
    return foodNames.filter(name => name.toLowerCase().includes(inputLower)).slice(0, 8);
  };

  // Autocomplete input component
  const FoodInput = ({ label, value, setValue, placeholder }) => {
    const [showSuggestions, setShowSuggestions] = useState(false);
    const suggestions = getSuggestions(value);

    const handleSelect = (suggestion) => {
      setValue(suggestion);
      setShowSuggestions(false);
    };

    return (
      <li style={{ marginBottom: '12px' }}>
        <strong>{label}:</strong>
        <div style={{ position: 'relative', display: 'inline-block', marginLeft: '10px' }}>
          <input
            type="text"
            placeholder={placeholder}
            value={value}
            onChange={e => {
              setValue(e.target.value);
              setShowSuggestions(true);
            }}
            onFocus={() => setShowSuggestions(true)}
            onBlur={() => setTimeout(() => setShowSuggestions(false), 150)}
            style={{ width: '200px', padding: '4px' }}
          />
          {showSuggestions && suggestions.length > 0 && (
            <ul style={{
              position: 'absolute',
              top: '100%',
              left: 0,
              right: 0,
              background: '#fff',
              border: '1px solid #ccc',
              borderRadius: '4px',
              listStyle: 'none',
              margin: 0,
              padding: 0,
              zIndex: 100,
              maxHeight: '180px',
              overflowY: 'auto',
              boxShadow: '0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15)'
            }}>
              {suggestions.map((s, idx) => (
                <li
                  key={idx}
                  onMouseDown={() => handleSelect(s)}
                  style={{
                    padding: '8px 12px',
                    cursor: 'pointer',
                    borderBottom: '1px solid #eee',
                    background: '#fff'
                  }}
                  onMouseOver={e => e.currentTarget.style.background = '#f0f0f0'}
                  onMouseOut={e => e.currentTarget.style.background = '#fff'}
                >
                  {s}
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          )}
        </div>
        {value && (
          <div style={{ color: '#555', marginTop: 4, marginLeft: '10px' }}>Entered: {value}</div>
        )}
      </li>
    );
  };

  return (
    <div>
      <h2>Your Dashboard</h2>
      <p>Goal: {goal || 'Not set'}</p>
      <div style={{marginTop: '20px'}}>
        <h3>Food</h3>
        <ul style={{ listStyleType: 'none', paddingLeft: 0 }}>
          <FoodInput label="Morning" value={morningFood} setValue={setMorningFood} placeholder="Enter morning food" />
          <FoodInput label="Evening" value={eveningFood} setValue={setEveningFood} placeholder="Enter evening food" />
          <FoodInput label="Post Evening" value={postEveningFood} setValue={setPostEveningFood} placeholder="Enter post evening food" />
          <FoodInput label="Night" value={nightFood} setValue={setNightFood} placeholder="Enter night food" />
        </ul>
        {(morningFood && eveningFood && postEveningFood && nightFood) && (
          <button style={{marginTop: '16px', padding: '8px 16px', fontSize: '16px'}} onClick={handleCalculate}>Calculate</button>
        )}
      </div>
      {results && <FoodResultsDashboard results={results} />}
    </div>
  );
}

export default Dashboard;
